---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
const updated = 'June 2026';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Watsons Interiors collects, uses and protects your information.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow prose">
      <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Privacy Policy' }]} />
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><em>Last updated: {updated}</em></p>

      <p>This Privacy Policy explains how {SITE.name} ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses and
      safeguards information when you visit <strong>{SITE.domain}</strong> (the "Site"). By using
      the Site, you consent to the practices described here.</p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Information you provide:</strong> when you subscribe to our newsletter or use our
        contact form, we collect details such as your name and email address.</li>
        <li><strong>Automatically collected data:</strong> like most websites, we automatically receive
        information such as your IP address, browser type, device, referring pages and the pages you
        view. This is collected via cookies and similar technologies.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>Cookies are small files stored on your device. We use them to understand how the Site is used,
      remember preferences, and serve relevant advertising. You can disable cookies in your browser
      settings, though some features may not function as intended.</p>

      <h2>Google AdSense &amp; third-party advertising</h2>
      <p>We use third-party advertising companies, including <strong>Google AdSense</strong>, to serve
      ads when you visit the Site. These companies may use cookies and web beacons to measure ad
      performance and show ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads on this Site.</li>
        <li>Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your
        visits to the Site and/or other sites on the internet.</li>
        <li>You may opt out of personalised advertising by visiting
        <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.</li>
        <li>You can also opt out of third-party vendor cookies at
        <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">aboutads.info/choices</a>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>We may use analytics services (such as Google Analytics) to understand site traffic and usage
      patterns in aggregate. These services may set their own cookies. The data helps us improve our
      content and user experience.</p>

      <h2>How we use information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To operate, maintain and improve the Site and its content.</li>
        <li>To send our newsletter and respond to your enquiries (only where you've opted in).</li>
        <li>To display relevant advertising and measure its performance.</li>
        <li>To detect, prevent and address technical or security issues.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Sharing of information</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with trusted service providers
      (such as email and advertising partners) only as needed to operate the Site, and with
      authorities where required by law.</p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct or delete your personal
      information, or to opt out of certain processing. To exercise these rights, contact us at
      <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>. Australian users are protected under the
      <em>Privacy Act 1988 (Cth)</em>.</p>

      <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>The Site is not directed at children under 16, and we do not knowingly collect personal
      information from them.</p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes take effect when posted on this page with
      a revised "last updated" date.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy? Email <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a> or use our
      <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
